## Project Overview
- **Mobile-first React + TypeScript web app for phones**
- Mobile responsiveness is the HIGHEST priority
- Stack: Bun + React 19 + TanStack Router/Query + Tailwind CSS v4

## Key Rules Summary
- Design for MOBILE first (44px touch targets, single column layouts)
- Page components in `src/components/[page-name]/` folders
- ALL API calls use TanStack Query with loading states
- All API payloads need Zod schemas in `src/schemas/`
- Use `zod.safeParse()` for validation
- Form errors appear directly below fields
- Centralized endpoints in `src/lib/api-endpoints.ts`
- Code style: no semicolons, double quotes, 2-space tabs

## Commands
```bash
bun install && bun run dev    # Start development
bun run lint:fix              # Fix code issues
bun run format                # Format code
```

# shadcn instructions

Use the latest version of Shadcn to install new components, like this command to add a button component:

```bash
bunx shadcn@latest add button
```

